
Ranger Help for: longfire
=========================

SYNTAX:      longfire <direction> at <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   14
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  bow

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to take advantage of the extra power
provided by the longbow. It allows a Ranger to shoot at targets
adjacent rooms. Being a long shot, its harder to hit, but the
arrows comes as a surprise to the target. Whatever the Ranger has
set as the longbow's loader will be used in longshot. The best arrow
in the loader will automatically be used in the shot.

